      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests and method-of-manufactured-solutions verification required for all relevant transport equations including hemolysis damage model.",
      "rationale": "Code verification was performed only for the Navier-Stokes solver; the hemolysis power-law damage model was not subjected to MMS verification. Achieved level 2 insufficient for required level 4."
