      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent grid convergence index must be computed on hemolysis index QoI across at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study completed; GCI on hemolysis index is 8.3%, exceeding the 5% threshold required at level 4. Spatial discretization error remains a gap for absolute hemolysis prediction."
