      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must use the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under VAD-representative operating conditions; scaled or simplified geometries are not acceptable at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Validation dataset used a simplified volute geometry differing from the FDA generic pump impeller clearance. Operating speeds were limited to 2500–3500 RPM; VAD COU requires coverage to 4500 RPM. Achieved level 2."
    },
