      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples must be characterised for lot-to-lot variability in blood properties; minimum n=5 independent replicates per operating point required for statistical comparison at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Experimental data drawn from a single blood lot with n=2 replicates at most operating points. Inter-lot variability in RBC fragility not characterised. Sample representativeness insufficient for MRL 5; flagged as epistemic gap."
